The '''<tt>%querytabled</tt>''' directive starts a query using Twelf's [[tabled logic programming]] engine, so that instances of a type family marked with <tt>[[%tabled]]</tt> directive will be derived at most once during proof search. It otherwise looks the same as <tt>[[%query]]</tt>.

