The '''<tt>%subord</tt>''' declaration adds edges to the [[subordination]] relation.  This declaration is currently only available in Twelf CVS{{discuss|Version}} and may not yet be available in [[TwelfTag]]. 

== Syntax ==

The syntax is as follows:

<tt>%subord (t1 t1') ... (tn tn').</tt>

The type families <tt>ti'</tt> will then be treated as being dependent on the type family <tt>ti</tt>.

